rows.label: bf08400100_0030
rows.name:
So this is what the World
Tree truly looks like...

rows.label: bf08400100_0040
rows.name:
Wait, those aren't leaves... Are
those some kind of symbols?

rows.label: bf08400100_0060
rows.name:
An Iiran battleship? I didn't think
any of those were still around.

rows.label: bf08400100_0080
rows.name:
I've never heard that
Acedia can fly this high.

rows.label: bf08400100_0090
rows.name: Cloud Sea so very far down below, mo!

rows.label: bf08400100_0100
rows.name:
Just like with Temperantia, they must
be controlling a Divine Beast somehow.

rows.label: bf08400100_0120
rows.name:
I never would have guessed
Acedia had such armaments.

rows.label: bf08400100_0130
rows.name:
Asking "what for" would be a
stupid question, wouldn't it?

rows.label: bf08400100_0140
rows.name:
They anticipated it. That Shin
and Metsu would try to ascend.

rows.label: bf08400100_0150
rows.name: So Shin is inside that massive vessel?

rows.label: bf08400100_0170
rows.name:
We need to hurry! If they make
it to Eden, Alst will be...

rows.label: bf08400100_0180
rows.name:
How do we get up there though?
The anchor's not going to reach.

rows.label: bf08400100_0190
rows.name: Let's just get as close as we can.
